  "justFinishedAt": "2026-03-14T18:33:51.023Z",
  "summary": "## Summary: Implement AI Support Chat Widget — Phase 1 MVP\n\n### Changes Implemented\n\n**Subsystem 1: Knowledge Base Ingestion Pipeline**\n- Built `lib/support/kb-ingest.ts` with all 6 ingestion methods: single URL, multi-page crawl, PDF text, direct text, CSV, and XML sitemap\n- Sentence-boundary-aware text chunking (~512 tokens per chunk)\n- OpenAI text-embedding-3-small integration with batch processing (20 per batch)\n- HTML stripping (removes scripts, styles, nav, footer, header) and internal link discovery for crawling\n- Source status tracking (queued → processing → complete/failed)\n- Toggle enabled/disabled on sources and their chunks\n\n**Subsystem 2: AI Chat Engine (RAG + Master Prompt)**\n- Built `lib/support/chat-engine.ts` with full RAG pipeline\n- Configurable master prompt stored in DB (editable without redeploy)\n- pgvector cosine similarity search (top K=5 chunks, 0.3 threshold)\n- Claude Sonnet 4 via OpenRouter for inference\n- Graceful fallback when no relevant chunks found or API fails\n- Session creation with metadata (pageUrl, userAgent, referrer)\n- Message persistence before returning response\n\n**Subsystem 3: Widget Embed & Visual Customization**\n- Built `components/support/SupportChatWidget.tsx` — full React widget with:\n  - Floating bubble (configurable size, color, position)\n  - Chat panel with welcome screen, starter buttons, markdown rendering\n  - Typing indicator, auto-scroll, session persistence via sessionStorage\n  - Full keyboard navigation (Enter/Space toggle, Escape close, focus trap)\n  - ARIA compliance (role=dialog, aria-labels, aria-live region)\n  - Dark mode support via CSS custom properties\n- Built `public/widget/support-chat.js` — standalone embed script for external sites\n  - Self-contained, style-isolated, works via `<script>` tag\n  - Fetches config from API, renders widget, handles chat flow\n- Integrated widget into marketing layout via dynamic import\n\n**Subsystem 4: Conversation History & Admin Viewer**\n- Admin conversation viewer with paginated sessions list and detail view\n- Session metadata display (page URL, user agent, timestamps)\n- Markdown rendering for assistant messages in admin viewer\n\n**Database Schema (additive only)**\n- `support_widget_config` — single-row config table (JSONB config + text masterPrompt)\n- `support_kb_sources` — knowledge base sources with status tracking\n- `support_kb_chunks` — embedded text chunks with pgvector HNSW index\n- `support_chat_sessions` — chat sessions with JSONB metadata\n- `support_chat_messages` — messages with role enum (user/assistant)\n- All with proper relations, indexes, and Drizzle ORM definitions\n- Migration: `0054_support-chat-widget.sql` with default config seed data\n\n**Admin Panel**\n- Dashboard page with links to KB, Config, and Conversations sub-pages\n- Knowledge Base management: ingestion form (URL/text/file), sources list with status badges, enable/disable toggle, delete\n- Widget Config: all visual settings with live preview, master prompt editor, embed code generator\n- Conversations viewer: paginated session list, drill-down message thread view\n\n**API Routes (9 total, all new)**\n- `POST /api/support-chat/session` — create session (public)\n- `POST /api/support-chat/message` — send message + RAG response (public)\n- `GET /api/support-chat/widget-config` — widget configuration (public)\n- `GET/POST /api/admin/support/kb` — list/create KB sources (admin)\n- `DELETE/PATCH /api/admin/support/kb/[sourceId]` — manage sources (admin)\n- `POST /api/admin/support/kb/upload` — file upload ingestion (admin)\n- `GET/PUT /api/admin/support/config` — widget config management (admin)\n- `GET /api/admin/support/conversations` — paginated session list (admin)\n- `GET /api/admin/support/conversations/[sessionId]` — session detail (admin)\n\n### Files Modified\n- `lib/db/schema.ts` — added 5 new tables, 3 enums, relations\n- `app/(marketing)/layout.tsx` — added SupportChatWidget via dynamic import\n- `components/ui/SideNav.tsx` — added Support Chat admin nav item + icon\n\n### Files Created\n- `drizzle/migrations/0054_support-chat-widget.sql`\n- `lib/support/kb-ingest.ts`\n- `lib/support/chat-engine.ts`\n- `app/api/support-chat/session/route.ts`\n- `app/api/support-chat/message/route.ts`\n- `app/api/support-chat/widget-config/route.ts`\n- `app/api/admin/support/kb/route.ts`\n- `app/api/admin/support/kb/[sourceId]/route.ts`\n- `app/api/admin/support/kb/upload/route.ts`\n- `app/api/admin/support/config/route.ts`\n- `app/api/admin/support/conversations/route.ts`\n- `app/api/admin/support/conversations/[sessionId]/route.ts`\n- `components/support/SupportChatWidget.tsx`\n- `public/widget/support-chat.js`\n- `app/(app)/admin/support/page.tsx`\n- `app/(app)/admin/support/knowledge-base/page.tsx`\n- `app/(app)/admin/support/knowledge-base/KnowledgeBaseClient.tsx`\n- `app/(app)/admin/support/config/page.tsx`\n- `app/(app)/admin/support/config/WidgetConfigClient.tsx`\n- `app/(app)/admin/support/conversations/page.tsx`\n- `app/(app)/admin/support/conversations/ConversationsClient.tsx`\n\n### Notes for Developer\n- **Migration**: Run `0054_support-chat-widget.sql` against your database. It requires the `pgvector` extension (creates if not exists).\n- **Environment variables**: Requires `OPENAI_API_KEY` for embeddings and `OPENROUTER_API_KEY` for Claude inference. Both should already be configured.\n- **No RLS on support tables**: The support chat tables are intentionally public (no auth required for widget visitors). Admin routes use `getRequiredAdmin()` for protection.\n- **Phase 2 compatibility**: The `support_chat_messages` table has a nullable `token_count` column ready for Phase 2 analytics. The schema supports adding a `corrections` column without breaking changes.\n- **Embed script**: The standalone script at `/widget/support-chat.js` can be used on external sites. The admin panel generates the correct `<script>` tag.\n- **TypeScript**: Zero new type errors — `tsc --noEmit` passes clean."
}